<!-- ファイル名: gift-settings-cart-integration.liquid -->
<!-- カート画面でのギフト設定表示スニペット -->
<!-- 使用方法: {% render 'gift-settings-cart-integration', item: cart_item %} -->

{%- comment -%}
  このスニペットは、カート内のアイテムにギフト設定プロパティが
  含まれている場合に、その内容を表示します。
  
  パラメータ:
  - item: カートアイテム（必須）
  - show_edit_link: 編集リンクを表示するか（オプション、デフォルト: false）
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  # ギフト設定プロパティの確認
  assign gift_quantity = item.properties['ギフト設定_数量']
  assign gift_purpose = item.properties['ギフト設定_用途']
  assign gift_addressee = item.properties['ギフト設定_宛名書き']
  assign gift_completed = item.properties['ギフト設定_完了']
  assign gift_timestamp = item.properties['ギフト設定_タイムスタンプ']
  assign gift_product_id = item.properties['ギフト設定_商品ID']
  
  # ギフト設定が存在するかチェック
  assign has_gift_settings = false
  if gift_completed == 'true' and gift_quantity != blank and gift_purpose != blank
    assign has_gift_settings = true
  endif
-%}

{%- if has_gift_settings -%}
  <div class="cart-gift-settings" data-cart-item-id="{{ item.id }}">
    
    <!-- ギフト設定ヘッダー -->
    <div class="cart-gift-header">
      <h4 class="cart-gift-title">
        <svg class="cart-gift-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M20 12v10H4V12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M22 7H2v5h20V7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M12 22V7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M12 7H7.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5C11 2 12 7 12 7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M12 7h4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5C13 2 12 7 12 7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        ギフト設定
      </h4>
      
      {%- if show_edit_link and gift_product_id -%}
        <a href="{{ routes.products_url }}/{{ all_products[gift_product_id].handle }}" 
           class="cart-gift-edit-link"
           aria-label="ギフト設定を編集">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          編集
        </a>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    <!-- ギフト設定詳細 -->
    <div class="cart-gift-details">
      
      <!-- 数量 -->
      <div class="cart-gift-detail-item">
        <span class="cart-gift-label">数量:</span>
        <span class="cart-gift-value">{{ gift_quantity }}</span>
      </div>

      <!-- 用途 -->
      <div class="cart-gift-detail-item">
        <span class="cart-gift-label">用途:</span>
        <span class="cart-gift-value">{{ gift_purpose }}</span>
      </div>

      <!-- 宛名書き（設定されている場合のみ） -->
      {%- if gift_addressee != blank -%}
        <div class="cart-gift-detail-item">
          <span class="cart-gift-label">宛名書き:</span>
          <span class="cart-gift-value">{{ gift_addressee }}</span>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      <!-- 設定日時（管理者用、設定で非表示にすることも可能） -->
      {%- if gift_timestamp != blank and settings.show_gift_timestamp -%}
        <div class="cart-gift-detail-item cart-gift-timestamp">
          <span class="cart-gift-label">設定日時:</span>
          <span class="cart-gift-value">
            <time datetime="{{ gift_timestamp }}">
              {{ gift_timestamp | date: '%Y年%m月%d日 %H:%M' }}
            </time>
          </span>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
      
    </div>

    <!-- 注意書き -->
    <div class="cart-gift-notice">
      <p class="cart-gift-notice-text">
        <svg class="cart-gift-notice-icon" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          <path d="M12 16v-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M12 8h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        上記の設定でギフト梱包いたします
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ギフト設定専用CSS -->
  <style>
    .cart-gift-settings {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 12px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .cart-gift-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }

    .cart-gift-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #007c89;
    }

    .cart-gift-icon {
      color: #007c89;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .cart-gift-edit-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      color: #007c89;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #007c89;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .cart-gift-edit-link:hover {
      background-color: #007c89;
      color: white;
    }

    .cart-gift-details {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .cart-gift-detail-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .cart-gift-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #495057;
      min-width: 80px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .cart-gift-value {
      color: #212529;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .cart-gift-timestamp {
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .cart-gift-notice {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }

    .cart-gift-notice-text {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6c757d;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .cart-gift-notice-icon {
      color: #6c757d;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* レスポンシブ対応 */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .cart-gift-settings {
        padding: 12px;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      .cart-gift-header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .cart-gift-edit-link {
        align-self: flex-end;
      }

      .cart-gift-detail-item {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .cart-gift-label {
        min-width: auto;
      }
    }
  </style>

{%- endif -%}